## 4. File Permissions

| Permission | Symbol | Value |
|------------|--------|-------|
| Read | `r` | 4 |
| Write | `w` | 2 |
| Execute | `x` | 1 |

> Examples:  
> `rwx = 7`, `rw- = 6`, `r-- = 4`, `--- = 0`

| Command | Description | Example |
|---------|-------------|---------|
| `chmod <mode> <file>` | Change file permissions | `chmod 755 script.sh` |
| `chown <user>:<group> <file>` | Change file owner/group | `chown test:IT file.txt` |

